            <h2><img src="/images/contact.png" alt="contact" class="icon">Get In Touch</h2>
            <div class="line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="say-hello-card">
            <p>I'm currently open for new opportunities. Whether you have a question or just want to say hi, I'll try my best to get back to you!</p>
            <button class="say-hello-btn">Say Hello</button>
